Package org.linguatools.stem.ar

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArNormalAnalyzer
    Calls Lucene's StandardTokenizer with ArabicNormalizationFilter to split the input text into normalized tokens.
    ArStemPretokAnalyzer
    Stems pre-tokenized input using WhitespaceAnalyzer and ArabicStemmer from Lucene.
    ArTokenAnalyzer
    Calls Lucene's StandardTokenizer to split the input text into tokens.
